## Naming Conventions

| Context | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Python files | snake_case | `review_service.py` |
| Python classes | PascalCase | `ReviewService` |
| Python functions | snake_case | `run_full_review()` |
| Python constants | UPPER_SNAKE | `CATEGORY_MAX` |
| React components | PascalCase | `IssueList.jsx` |
| React props | camelCase | `onSubmit`, `includeBenchmark` |
| CSS classes | kebab-case | `.issue-card` |
| DB tables | plural snake_case | `benchmark_runs` |
| DB columns | snake_case | `review_id`, `created_at` |
| API routes | plural kebab | `/reviews/`, `/benchmark-runs/` |

