## Scoring System Reference

Category weights (max points):
- correctness: 4000
- security: 2000
- maintainability: 2000
- test_coverage: 1000
- documentation: 1000

Severity multipliers:
- critical: 1.0 (100% of category max)
- major: 0.4 (40%)
- minor: 0.13 (13%)
- info: 0.0 (0%)

Each category is independently floored at 0.
